IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. TEMP-CONVERT.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 CELSIUS PIC S9(3)V9 VALUE 25.0.
       01 FAHRENHEIT PIC S9(3)V9 VALUE 0.
       01 KELVIN PIC 9(4)V9 VALUE 0.
       01 TEMP-COUNTER PIC 9(2) VALUE 0.
       01 MAX-TEMPS PIC 9(2) VALUE 5.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-CONVERTER.
           PERFORM PROCESS-TEMPS UNTIL TEMP-COUNTER >= MAX-TEMPS.
           STOP RUN.

       PROCESS-TEMPS.
           ADD 1 TO TEMP-COUNTER.
           ADD 5 TO CELSIUS.
           PERFORM CONVERT-TO-FAHRENHEIT.
           PERFORM CONVERT-TO-KELVIN.
           PERFORM DISPLAY-RESULTS.

       CONVERT-TO-FAHRENHEIT.
           COMPUTE FAHRENHEIT = CELSIUS * 9 / 5 + 32.

       CONVERT-TO-KELVIN.
           COMPUTE KELVIN = CELSIUS + 273.15.

       DISPLAY-RESULTS.
           DISPLAY "Temperature Conversion".
           DISPLAY "Celsius".
           DISPLAY CELSIUS.
           DISPLAY "Fahrenheit".
           DISPLAY FAHRENHEIT.
           DISPLAY "Kelvin".
           DISPLAY KELVIN.